9 COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 1158, L.D. 1740, “An Act to Establish
10 the Maine Science, Technology, Engineering, Arts and Mathematics Matching Grant
11 Program”
12 Amend the bill by striking out the title and substituting the following:
13 'An Act to Establish the Science, Technology, Engineering, Arts and Mathematics
14 Education Matching Grant Program'
15 Amend the bill in section 1 in c. 335 in §9942 by inserting after subsection 1 the
16 following:
17 '2. Administrative costs. Funds received for the grant program may be used by the
18 department for administrative costs of the grant program.'
19 Amend the bill in section 1 in c. 335 in §9942 by renumbering the subsections to read
20 consecutively.
21 Amend the bill by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or section
22 number to read consecutively.
23 SUMMARY
2244 This amendment is the majority report of the committee. The amendment provides that
2255 the Department of Education may use funds in the Science, Technology, Engineering, Arts
2266 and Mathematics Education Matching Grant Program for administrative costs of the
2277 program. The amendment also changes the title.
